{"tid":41870,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"ex想約我食飯，去唔去好？","createTime":"2016-12-16T08:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T11:51:01.000Z","uid":12068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ede314cfe1661f887706b236917d30cd1dad71c","tid":41870,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"同佢分開咗年幾兩年，從對話感覺中我feel到佢仲好鍾意我，<br />\n我自己已經有個都幾穩定嘅曖昧對象，我唔係好想同佢食呢餐，驚有咩誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但佢已不下約咗我十次或以上，我都係 No曬，今次佢好似特別唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應該繼續no落去定同佢食一餐再講清楚？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 佢地兩個女人大家都唔知大家嘅存在"},{"pid":"a12e13929048aef22e6de2b45bdfde5a5c534631","tid":41870,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a58d830fe9431c176bad6d2f50a35acdde91f0","tid":41870,"uid":16253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"e8dd9d479daf70cd98aa5721543d07d8c2e7a7b4","tid":41870,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"決絕d啦"},{"pid":"f6561ff3a71c0d16e5ec935f58ff5167a65cdb81","tid":41870,"uid":343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"都拒絕咗十幾次 唔爭在拒絕埋呢次啦"},{"pid":"af7b4a27822944fb4cb52ffa6d56b524a32f9117","tid":41870,"uid":66305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:37:43.000Z","msg":"之前咩事分手？"},{"pid":"ed194f601f3e0668da731320904ccc6330a2f670","tid":41870,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"咩叫做幾穩定既曖昧對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787