e":"2016-12-16T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去食一餐可能改變你嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 我驚我忍唔住手 食埋佢<br />\n跟住又有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec05c4e4a08ff929c5fc0107f41091517ee9f59","tid":41870,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前咩事分手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係大家淡咗，成日嘈，日日懷疑對方有第二個咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3161f64673a352a5c72f977a7e3582793e06eade","tid":41870,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"留名睇兩頭唔到岸<br />\n最尾乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35a8ecd82246b9b38ff6af6a8d234ed9bcb71b4","tid":41870,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇兩頭唔到岸<br />\n最尾乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c083bbb2ff6cdd61805783765e899676402a5e6","tid":41870,"uid":24943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去食一餐可能改變你嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 我驚我忍唔住手 食埋佢<br />\n跟住又有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食埋唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e9921aacc57eb7f550cccf319b7c6b81a0f302","tid":41870,"uid":58687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"二選一啦樓主<br />\n同ex咁樣玩落去只係畀假希望佢<br />\n你可憐佢嘅，斬斷情絲好過啦<br />\n(除非你仲鍾意人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f5d3c36e7571811aa7ae49333220f901e34ac668","tid":41870,"uid":336